<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201014/06b02984b2034427927137dee9553ac7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（来源：金龙鱼公告）</strong></p>
